<title type="html"><![CDATA[Settings of «Info-Center»]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?t=7041&amp;p=30215#p30215"><![CDATA[
Hi<br /><br />My language is German. Home in Switzerland. System Win10. Latest updates installed. Classic Shell 4.3.0. Default settings only.<br /><br />1. If I'd read everything I'm supposed to, it's gona take me ages. Sorry, I try to find solutions, not to do studies on Forums.<br /><br />2. Forum Search on «Info-Center» (as shown on, at least German version of Windows 10) does NOT show result of «Info-Center» but of entries containing words «Info» and «Center».<br /><br />3. Forum Search on «Infocenter» (my own idea!?!) results in no result/match at all.<br /><br />***<br /><br />According to page: <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://support.microsoft.com/de-de/help/10761/windows-10-change-notification-action-settings">https://support.microsoft.com/de-de/hel ... n-settings</a><!-- m --><br /><br />I'm supposed to go for «<span style="font-size: 100%; line-height: 116%;"><strong><span style="font-family:Segoe UI, Segoe UI Web, Segoe UI Symbol, Helvetica Neue, BBAlpha Sans, S60 Sans, Arial, sans-serif;">Start</span></strong><span style="font-family:Segoe UI, Segoe UI Web, Segoe UI Symbol, Helvetica Neue, BBAlpha Sans, S60 Sans, Arial, sans-serif;"></span><span style="font-family:Dev Center MDL2 Assets, Membership MDL2 Assets;"></span><span style="font-family:Segoe UI, Segoe UI Web, Segoe UI Symbol, Helvetica Neue, BBAlpha Sans, S60 Sans, Arial, sans-serif;">und dann</span><strong><span style="font-family:Segoe UI, Segoe UI Web, Segoe UI Symbol, Helvetica Neue, BBAlpha Sans, S60 Sans, Arial, sans-serif;">Einstellungen &#40;Symbol: Zahnrad&#41;</span></strong><span style="font-family:Segoe UI, Segoe UI Web, Segoe UI Symbol, Helvetica Neue, BBAlpha Sans, S60 Sans, Arial, sans-serif;"></span><span style="font-family:Dev Center MDL2 Assets, Membership MDL2 Assets;"></span><span style="font-family:Segoe UI, Segoe UI Web, Segoe UI Symbol, Helvetica Neue, BBAlpha Sans, S60 Sans, Arial, sans-serif;">&gt;</span><strong><span style="font-family:Segoe UI, Segoe UI Web, Segoe UI Symbol, Helvetica Neue, BBAlpha Sans, S60 Sans, Arial, sans-serif;">System</span></strong><span style="font-family:Segoe UI, Segoe UI Web, Segoe UI Symbol, Helvetica Neue, BBAlpha Sans, S60 Sans, Arial, sans-serif;">&gt;</span><strong><span style="font-family:Segoe UI, Segoe UI Web, Segoe UI Symbol, Helvetica Neue, BBAlpha Sans, S60 Sans, Arial, sans-serif;">Benachrichtigungen und Infos</span></strong></span>».<br /><br />(Translation: «<span style="font-size: 100%; line-height: 116%;"><strong><span style="font-family:Segoe UI, Segoe UI Web, Segoe UI Symbol, Helvetica Neue, BBAlpha Sans, S60 Sans, Arial, sans-serif;">Start</span></strong><span style="font-family:Segoe UI, Segoe UI Web, Segoe UI Symbol, Helvetica Neue, BBAlpha Sans, S60 Sans, Arial, sans-serif;"></span><span style="font-family:Segoe UI, Segoe UI Web, Segoe UI Symbol, Helvetica Neue, BBAlpha Sans, S60 Sans, Arial, sans-serif;">and then</span><strong><span style="font-family:Segoe UI, Segoe UI Web, Segoe UI Symbol, Helvetica Neue, BBAlpha Sans, S60 Sans, Arial, sans-serif;">Settings &#40;Icon: cogwheel&#41;</span></strong><span style="font-family:Segoe UI, Segoe UI Web, Segoe UI Symbol, Helvetica Neue, BBAlpha Sans, S60 Sans, Arial, sans-serif;"></span><span style="font-family:Dev Center MDL2 Assets, Membership MDL2 Assets;"></span><span style="font-family:Segoe UI, Segoe UI Web, Segoe UI Symbol, Helvetica Neue, BBAlpha Sans, S60 Sans, Arial, sans-serif;">&gt;</span><strong><span style="font-family:Segoe UI, Segoe UI Web, Segoe UI Symbol, Helvetica Neue, BBAlpha Sans, S60 Sans, Arial, sans-serif;">System</span></strong><span style="font-family:Segoe UI, Segoe UI Web, Segoe UI Symbol, Helvetica Neue, BBAlpha Sans, S60 Sans, Arial, sans-serif;">&gt;</span><strong><span style="font-family:Segoe UI, Segoe UI Web, Segoe UI Symbol, Helvetica Neue, BBAlpha Sans, S60 Sans, Arial, sans-serif;">Messages and Infos</span></strong></span>».)<br /><br />However, on my Start-Menu, there is only «(Symbol: Zahnrad) Einstellungen» (Translation: «(Icon: cogwheel) Settings». BTW: cogwheel comes before word of settings and not after, as shown of Microsofts «manual-page».<br /><br />On «(Symbol: Zahnrad) Einstellungen» there is no Option «System». Only option that comes close to that is «Systemsteuerung» («System control»), whereafter all possible Settings of Windows (approx. 49 items). But none of them is named «Benachrichtigungen und Infos» nor one of these two words or something that comes close to, not even in the sense of.<br /><br />Entry of «Info» in start-menus search field gives in (third section only) «PC-Einstellungen (16)» (PC-Settings (16)) option to change color of Start-Menu, Taskbar and Info-Center<br />Another option of that search-result gives opportunity to change transparency of Info-Center.<br /><br />Finally, only entry of «Benachrichtigungen» in start-menus search field seems to leed to «Einstellungen für Benachrichtigungen und Aktionen» (Settings for Messages and Actions) where setting searched for can be made. BTW Infos is not equal to Actions.<br /><br />***<br /><br />After having done still quite a lot of work ...<br /><br />Q: Why do I not find «<span style="font-size: 100%; line-height: 116%;"><strong><span style="font-family:Segoe UI, Segoe UI Web, Segoe UI Symbol, Helvetica Neue, BBAlpha Sans, S60 Sans, Arial, sans-serif;">Start</span></strong><span style="font-family:Segoe UI, Segoe UI Web, Segoe UI Symbol, Helvetica Neue, BBAlpha Sans, S60 Sans, Arial, sans-serif;"></span><span style="font-family:Dev Center MDL2 Assets, Membership MDL2 Assets;"></span><span style="font-family:Segoe UI, Segoe UI Web, Segoe UI Symbol, Helvetica Neue, BBAlpha Sans, S60 Sans, Arial, sans-serif;">und dann</span><strong><span style="font-family:Segoe UI, Segoe UI Web, Segoe UI Symbol, Helvetica Neue, BBAlpha Sans, S60 Sans, Arial, sans-serif;">Einstellungen &#40;Symbol: Zahnrad&#41;</span></strong><span style="font-family:Segoe UI, Segoe UI Web, Segoe UI Symbol, Helvetica Neue, BBAlpha Sans, S60 Sans, Arial, sans-serif;"></span><span style="font-family:Dev Center MDL2 Assets, Membership MDL2 Assets;"></span><span style="font-family:Segoe UI, Segoe UI Web, Segoe UI Symbol, Helvetica Neue, BBAlpha Sans, S60 Sans, Arial, sans-serif;">&gt;</span><strong><span style="font-family:Segoe UI, Segoe UI Web, Segoe UI Symbol, Helvetica Neue, BBAlpha Sans, S60 Sans, Arial, sans-serif;">System</span></strong><span style="font-family:Segoe UI, Segoe UI Web, Segoe UI Symbol, Helvetica Neue, BBAlpha Sans, S60 Sans, Arial, sans-serif;">&gt;</span><strong><span style="font-family:Segoe UI, Segoe UI Web, Segoe UI Symbol, Helvetica Neue, BBAlpha Sans, S60 Sans, Arial, sans-serif;">Benachrichtigungen und Infos</span></strong></span>» on Classic-Shell-Default-Menu? <br /><br />What am I doing wrong?<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=16006">tamaleus</a> — Fri Nov 04, 2016 10:32 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
